top.title=About this mod
top.str0=This mod is a tool helps creating PvE with command blocks in 1.12.2.
top.str1=Without changing basic ways in 1.12.2, it allows to create PvE using vanilla commands.
top.str2=
top.str3=Not only PvE, but you can also make PvP or other things. It's up to you!
top.str4=
top.str5=Operations:
top.str6=・Changing tabs: Click tabs in left.
