potions.title=Potion effects
potions.str0=This mod adds potion effects which is useful for combat.
potions.str1=You can give effects using
potions.str2=/effect [target] [name] [amplifier] [duration(s)]
potions.str3=command.
potions.str4=It also can be given as effect of potion items with /give command.
potions.str5=
potions.str6=※Described as amplifier with the amount incremented.
potions.str7=※Effect names are omitted namespace [bosscreatortool:].
potions.str8=use like:
potions.str9=/effect @p bosscreatortool:physical_1 4 1
potions.str10=
potions.str11=・Instant Damage
potions.str12= Deal various damage with a fixed amount. There are type 1-4 and damage amount is [amplifier]x1, [amplifier]x10, [amplifier]x100, [amplifier]x1000, respectively.
potions.str13= Effect names:
potions.str14= Physical: physical_[type]
potions.str15= Magic: magic_[type]
potions.str16= Fixed: void_[type]
potions.str17= Ignoring invinsiblity: true_[type]
potions.str18= Piercing: pierce_[type]
potions.str19= Healing: heal_[type]
potions.str20=
potions.str21=・Continuous Damage
potions.str22= Deal [amplifier] damages per second.
potions.str23= Effect names:
potions.str24= Poison: poison
potions.str25= Wither: wither
potions.str26= Fire: fire ※Cannot be removed with water.
potions.str27=
potions.str28=・Damage buff/debuff
potions.str29= Change damages deal/receive for [amplifier]%%.
potions.str30= Effect names:
potions.str31= Physical dealt:
potions.str32=  Increase: p_atk_up Decrease: p_atk_down
potions.str33= Magic dealt:
potions.str34=  Increase: p_atk_up Decrease: p_atk_down
potions.str35= Physical received:
potions.str36=  Increase: p_res_down Decrease: p_res_up
potions.str37= Magic received:
potions.str38=  Increase: p_res_down Decrease: p_res_up
potions.str39= ※Received damage effect has reversed up/down from dealt damage. up is buff and down is debuff.
