tags.title=Entity Tags
tags.str0=This mod allows to change stats of entities by changing tags. It enables to make a entity with stats which is impossible in vanilla.
tags.str1=To add entity tags:
tags.str2=/scoreboard players tag [target] add [tag]
tags.str3=To give tags on summon:
tags.str4=/summon [mob] [position] {Tags:["[tag]"]}
tags.str5=command.
tags.str6=
tags.str7=・Resistance
tags.str8= Changes entities' resistance. Formally, changes damage received to make the health to a fixed amount.
tags.str9= How to set:
tags.str10= Add tag "ehp:(amount)".
tags.str11= (Ex: ehp:2000)
tags.str12=
tags.str13=・Strength
tags.str14= Changes entities' melee damage.
tags.str15= How to set:
tags.str16= Add tag "damage:(amount)".
tags.str17= (Ex: damage:2000)

